trends: There have been 6 other sightings in Wasilla
There were no other sightings in Wasilla on or around January 23rd 2009
divs: Sighting DetailsI was just at a conference in Anchorage with my paranormal investigation team's booth. I was told that there have been a slew of sightings of glowing discs in the Mat-Su Valley, seen by folks in Anchorage and Wasilla. The same sort of objects have been seen recently in Fairbanks and North Pole (in the interior). We had three pictures from the Newsminer's webcam (ufo sightings found on MUFON) of an old ufo caught on film. Many people said that the glowing discs look exactly as the glowing disc from the newsminer's photos look.
